column16: Xander Bogaerts flies out to right fielder Nelson Cruz.
Brock Holt singles on a line drive to left fielder Franklin Gutierrez.   Mookie Betts to 2nd.
Mookie Betts singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Franklin Gutierrez.
Jackie Bradley homers (4) on a fly ball to right center field.    Blake Swihart scores.
Blake Swihart doubles (12) on a fly ball to center fielder Austin Jackson.   Josh Rutledge scores.
Alejandro De Aza lines out to right fielder Nelson Cruz.
Josh Rutledge singles on a ground ball to left fielder Franklin Gutierrez.
Travis Shaw flies out to left fielder Franklin Gutierrez.
Jake Marisnick grounds out, shortstop Brad Miller to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Preston Tucker grounds into a double play, third baseman Kyle Seager to second baseman Willie Bloomquist to first baseman Logan Morrison.   Marwin Gonzalez out at 2nd.
